<plot>Far too neurotic to actually go on a date, Asimov451 and FuturaMaria are two socially challenged geniuses seeking to unravel the mysteries of lucrative courting. The two pit their dating androids, Clyde and Guenevere, in a synthetic battle of the sexes. Stumbling their way through a series of dates and romantic misadventures, Clyde and Guenevere find there is more going on inside of them than just 1's and 0's. Unfortunately, their emotionally crippled creators can't allow anything to taint their pale portrait of love. Without mercy the scientists wage a war of insensitivity, infidelity, and breast augmentation. Can romance flourish in the face of artifice and cynicism? Love may be the one glitch they can't debug.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?129920</url></doc>
